							<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="50" />
						</svg>
						<img class="hero-image" src="hero-image.jpg" />
					</div>
					<div class="hero-text-container">
						<p class="greeting">
							Hi, I'm <span class="highlight">Aevan Josh.</span>
						</p>
						<p class="description">
							I am a
							<span class="highlight">front-end web developer</span>
							with a passion for thoughtful UI design. Seeking to gain industry
							experience in web development.
